import React from 'react'

export default function SignUp() {
    return (
        <>
            <VStack
                divider={<StackDivider borderColor='gray.200' />}
                spacing={4}
                align='stretch'
            >
                <Box h='40px' bg='yellow.200'>
                    1
                </Box>
                <Box h='40px' bg='tomato'>
                    2
                </Box>
                <Box h='40px' bg='pink.100'>
                    3
                </Box>
            </VStack>
        </>
    )
}
